Package: tidymirt
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Representations of Mirt Model Output
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Michael Chow
Maintainer: Michael Chow <michael@datacamp.com>
Description: Broom methods for working with fitted mirt models.
    These methods provide quick ways to summarize model fits (glance),
    get tibble representations of parameters (tidy), and return a
    model-enriched form of the data (augment; not yet implemented).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1),
    mirt,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    tidyr,
    stringr,
    broom
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Suggests: 
    testthat
